name: Space Fish (Snycent)
description:
You are a UFO  that now makes you an IFO (Identified flying object) lmao

Use your beam to grab as many fish as you can! You can shoot the bombs so you can grab even more fish!

Controls :

Z - Use tractor beam

X - Shoot photon torpedoes

This game was made for Mini Jam 91: UFO but in only 1.5 days 

Comment down below what you think of this type of game and if I should keep developing it any further
